test_cell: {"test_cell_metadata": {"cell_uuid": "85823e9d-fb61-44a9-8ef6-d169d6581cb7"}}
```
If I try to alter the meta-data using the cell tool in jupyterlab, then it fails to save changes when clicking on the save icon.

![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/4063815/24084966/ab31ffb0-0ceb-11e7-8587-324847a5c314.png)

